race.comment: WISECRACKER (1) collided with another runner and finished a well held 6 lengths fourth (17.72) last time in a Grade 5/6 at this track over 300m. Can find winning form here. MORPHIN GRID (3) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (17.30), beaten a neck. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Well placed and gets his chance. PRIDE AND POWER (2) missed the frame last time after colliding with another runner in a Grade 6 at Cannington, finishing a 5.5 lengths eighth (22.71). Better than last start and can bounce back. SQUEEZE LI (7) can play a role in the finish without surprising.
